name: MEEB Vault (NFTX)
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: MEEB Vault is an erc-20 vault token representing NFT assets within a NFTX Vault. Vault tokens allow NFTX to be a platform for creating liquid markets for illiquid Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs).
